Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:28.96,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2.5}te ni totte tashikameteta
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:30.96,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5}that there's definitely no going back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:30.96,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2.5}kitto modorenain datte
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:36.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5}Whose side are you o{\fsp5}n{\fnBohemian typewriter\fs49}?
