Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:48.97,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be1\c&HAC8455&}mujun haramu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.97,0:22:53.81,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1\c&H3C5B8B&}The sound of the scheme
